          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Don't want to log into 3 dashboards — just want results?</h4>
            <p>theStacc tracks GBP rank, calls, and reviews — then ships the weekly posts and photos that move those numbers. <strong>Local SEO from $49/mo</strong> — analytics and action under one bill.</p>
